org.eclipse.jdt.junit.model

Interface ITestElementContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITestElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ITestRunSession, ITestSuiteElement

    public interface ITestElementContainer
extends ITestElement
    Common protocol for test elements containers. This set consists of ITestSuiteElement and ITestRunSession

    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.

    Since:
    3.3
    Restriction:
    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.
